@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Statement - TM470 Grade Calculator";
}

<style>
    h1 {
        margin-bottom: 40px; 
    }
</style>

<body>
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <h2>1. Affiliation Disclaimer</h2>

    <div class="disclaimer">
        <p>This web application for calculating projected final grades for the TM470 module is a personal project. The creator of this application is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to The Open University in any official capacity. This tool is designed as an independent resource for students.</p>
        <p>The Calculation of the module grade is based on the Module guideline from 2024 and the Assignments are weighted as the following: TMA1 5%, TMA2 and TMA3 10% and the EMA is 75%.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>2. Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your data with transparency:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Data Collection:</strong> This application does not collect or store any personal information from its users. All calculations are performed locally in your web browser.</li>
        <li><strong>No Data Sharing:</strong> Since we do not collect any data, there is no information to share with third parties.</li>
        <li><strong>Changes to This Policy:</strong> If there are any future changes to how this application handles data, this privacy statement will be updated accordingly.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: <span id="current-date"></span></p>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('current-date').textContent = new Date().toDateString();
    </script>
</body>
